comment.author: 75445931@N06
comment._content: This is NC13993, s/n 2, the second production Spartan 7W "Executive" produced by the Spartan Aircraft Company in 1936. It rolled off of the lines on 11/30/1936. It is the oldest extant 7W, and currently resides at the EAA Museum in Oshkosh, Wisconsin. Beautiful shot! Do you have any idea about the ID of the photographer?
